_sText:
mg_vall is a course map, made in 21 levels, my idea was to create a map more rewarding than challenging. At the end of it are some experiments I would like to do with the map. Some of the challenges, or most of them, I tried to do differently or just get out of my head. Some are obviously inspired by other course maps already made.

• 21 Levels
• 1 Secret
• 1 Final
• Some smoke tracers on the map
